---
import DemoCamera from './DemoCamera.tsx'
---

<section class="bg-gradient-to-br from-gray-900 to-gray-800 text-white py-8 md:py-14">
  <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
    <div id="hero-grid" class="grid lg:grid-cols-2 gap-8 lg:gap-16 items-start">

      <!-- Esquerda: headline + CTAs -->
      <div class="lg:pt-4">
        <div class="inline-flex items-center gap-2 bg-orange-500/20 text-orange-300 px-4 py-1.5 rounded-full text-sm font-medium mb-5">
          <span>🤖</span>
          <span>Plataforma de Reconhecimento por IA</span>
        </div>

        <h1 class="text-3xl sm:text-4xl md:text-5xl font-bold mb-5 leading-tight">
          Reconheça qualquer objeto com as câmeras que
          <span class="text-orange-400"> você já tem</span>
        </h1>

        <p class="text-lg text-gray-300 mb-7 leading-relaxed">
          Visão computacional industrial em tempo real. EPIs, veículos, produtos —
          qualquer coisa que sua operação precisa monitorar, detectada automaticamente
          com modelos de IA treináveis.
        </p>

        <div class="flex flex-col sm:flex-row gap-3 mb-8">
          <a
            href="#hero-demo"
            class="px-7 py-3.5 bg-orange-500 text-white rounded-xl hover:bg-orange-600 transition font-semibold text-lg shadow-lg text-center"
          >
            🎯 Testar ao Vivo →
          </a>
          <a
            href="#modulos"
            class="px-7 py-3.5 border border-white/20 text-white rounded-xl hover:bg-white/10 transition font-semibold text-lg text-center"
          >
            Ver Módulos
          </a>
        </div>

        <div class="flex flex-wrap gap-x-6 gap-y-2 text-sm text-gray-400">
          <div class="flex items-center gap-2"><span class="text-green-400">✓</span> Sem hardware novo</div>
          <div class="flex items-center gap-2"><span class="text-green-400">✓</span> &lt;3s de latência</div>
          <div class="flex items-center gap-2"><span class="text-green-400">✓</span> Modelo customizável</div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- Direita / Baixo (mobile): Demo ao vivo -->
      <div id="hero-demo" class="w-full">
        <div class="bg-gray-800/60 rounded-2xl border border-gray-700 p-3 sm:p-4">
          <div class="flex items-center justify-between mb-3">
            <span class="text-sm font-semibold text-gray-300">Teste a IA agora mesmo</span>
            <span class="flex items-center gap-1.5 text-xs bg-red-500/20 text-red-400 px-2.5 py-1 rounded-full font-medium">
              <span class="w-1.5 h-1.5 bg-red-400 rounded-full animate-pulse"></span>
              Ao vivo
            </span>
          </div>

          <DemoCamera client:only="react" />
        </div>
      </div>

    </div>
  </div>
</section>
